{"action":"created","issue":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/issues/54099","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/issues/54099/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/issues/54099/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/issues/54099/events","html_url":"https://github.com/JuliaLang/julia/pull/54099","id":2245240680,"node_id":"PR_kwDOABkWpM5swqcM","number":54099,"title":"Add devdocs on UB","user":{"login":"Keno","id":1291671,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjEyOTE2NzE=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1291671?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/Keno","html_url":"https://github.com/Keno","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Keno/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Keno/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Keno/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Keno/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Keno/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Keno/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Keno/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Keno/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Keno/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"labels":[{"id":115619,"node_id":"MDU6TGFiZWwxMTU2MTk=","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/labels/doc","name":"doc","color":"02d7e1","default":false,"description":"This change adds or pertains to documentation"}],"state":"open","locked":false,"assignee":null,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":4,"created_at":"2024-04-16T06:42:12Z","updated_at":"2024-04-16T17:46:31Z","closed_at":null,"author_association":"MEMBER","active_lock_reason":null,"draft":false,"pull_request":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/pulls/54099","html_url":"https://github.com/JuliaLang/julia/pull/54099","diff_url":"https://github.com/JuliaLang/julia/pull/54099.diff","patch_url":"https://github.com/JuliaLang/julia/pull/54099.patch","merged_at":null},"body":"This adds some basic devdocs for undefined behavior, since there keep being complaints that it's not written down anywhere. The list of UB is just what I remembered off the top of my head, it's probably incomplete, since we haven't historically been particularly careful about this. This way, at least when people add new sources of UB, they'll have a centralized place to write that down.","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/issues/54099/reactions","total_count":3,"+1":2,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":1,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/issues/54099/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":null},"comment":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/issues/comments/2059634466","html_url":"https://github.com/JuliaLang/julia/pull/54099#issuecomment-2059634466","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/issues/54099","id":2059634466,"node_id":"IC_kwDOABkWpM56w4ci","user":{"login":"Seelengrab","id":11753998,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjExNzUzOTk4","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/11753998?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/Seelengrab","html_url":"https://github.com/Seelengrab","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Seelengrab/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Seelengrab/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Seelengrab/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Seelengrab/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Seelengrab/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Seelengrab/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Seelengrab/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Seelengrab/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Seelengrab/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2024-04-16T17:46:30Z","updated_at":"2024-04-16T17:46:30Z","author_association":"CONTRIBUTOR","body":"> My previous — obviously wrong — understanding was that the Julia compiler was trying to guard us from LLVM's undefined behaviors via freezes and such.

That is not so - admittedly, without a specified memory model it's a bit hard to do for everything in this PR (things involving pointers in particular, though those operations generally inherit the semantics of C by necessity), but in principle everything here can be justified as being in this document through Julia semantics alone. Undefined behavior is not something that bubbles up from a lower level of abstraction, but is inherent to _every_ level of abstraction, to some extent (and with sometimes more disliked behavior than other times). Getting an error when calling `lowercase` on a `String` containing malformed UTF-8 is just as much "undefined behavior" (in the sense that it's not defined what exactly happens when you try to do that) as misusing `@inbounds` is - the latter usually just has much more disastrous effects.

